                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Use at Your Own Risk:</strong> We are not responsible if a location is closed, full, or unsuitable upon your arrival. Always check Google Maps for real-time operating hours before traveling.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
